<%= section "Overview of topics" do %>

<p>The Topics section is where you will add links to course materials. You will organize and sequence these materials into groups, so that each group contains resources and exercises related to a particular <em>topic</em> taught in your course.</p>
  
<p>In <%= SITE_NAME %>, these "groups" of related exercises and resources are simply called <em>topics</em>. Eventually, you will use create assignments using these topics.<p>

<p>Before adding any content to your Topics section, your course materials must be hosted on on <%= link_to "Connexions", "http://www.cnx.org" %> and <%= link_to "Quadbase", "http://www.quadbase.org" %>. Check out our Class Planning guide for more help.</p> 
   
<% end %>

